baab -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qaybta ama badh hadal ah oo ka kooban sadar ama sadarro. Aan baab tusaale ah, ku bilaabe hadalkee, bismilaahi waa kow.
baab -ka: (magac, lab, keli) jaad turubka ah; afarta jaad ee turubka midkood. Dheeman iyo isbigmid kastaa waa baab.
baab -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qaybaha kitaab ama buug ka kooban yahay, qayb is ku hal ujeeddo ka hadlaysa. Dh: cutub, qayb.
baaba': (fal) raadkaa ba', madho oo ha jirin.
baaba' -a: (magac, lab, keli) wax tirtiran oo noqday wax aan jirin; wax aan muuqan oo raad lahayn. Baaba'a lo'da abaartaa keentay. Dh: dabargo'. Li: jirid, joogitaan.
baabah: (tilmaame) madhnaan; eber faaruq ah. Weelkii waa baabah oo waxba kuma hadhin. Dh: faaruq, madhan. Li: buux, budh.
baaban: (tilmaame) mid la baabay; mid la falay. Dh: falan, sixran, qataaran, maran.
baaba'san: (tilmaame) wax tirtiran; wax aan jirin. Raad baaba'san lama raaci karo.
baaba'sanaad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) noqoshada wax aan jirin; wax raq iyo ruux midna ka joogin.
baaba'sanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax aan jirin ahaan. Dh: baaba'sanaad.
baaba'sanaw: (fal) wax aan jirin ahaw; noqo wax baabba'ay.
baabasiir: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qanjidh xanuun ah oo siyaabo kala duwan futada ama walamadka uga soo baxa oo cidda uu ka soo baxo laga jeexo. Cali baabasiir ayaa laga gooyay. Dh: mabaasiir, babaasiir, bawaasiir.
baabbacay: (fal) geel, dhereg aawadii la orod oo cagaha dhulka la dhac. Geel baa ku baabbaceeyey adhi. Dh: baabbacee.
baabbacayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) geel, dhereg aawadii la ordid oo cagaha dhulka la dhicid. Baabbacayn geel baa ku jaba. Dh: durdurin.
baabbacee: (fal) geel, dhereg aawadii la orod oo cagaha dhulka la dhac. Dh: baabbacay.
baabbaco: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) orod dhereg aawadii geelu cagta hoose dhulka la dhaco.
baabbaco -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gacanta iyo lugta dadka inta ka soo hadha faraha iyo suulka. In aan Axmad guursadaa waa baabacadaa oo timo ka soo baxeen! Dh: sacab, calaacal.
baabbah: (tilmaame) aanay waxba ka jirin ama ku jirin; wax halna ka joogin ama ku jirin. Gorofku waa baabbah. Dh: madhan. Li: buuxa.
baabbahay: (fal) wax aan gudihisa wax ku jirin ka dhig: eber ka dhig. Dh: baabbahee, madhi, faaruqi, dhammee.
baabbahayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax aan gudihiisa wax ba ku jirin ama madhay ka dhigid.
baabba'san: (tilmaame) wax tirtiran oo aan waxba ka jirin. Dh: burbursan, tirtiran. Li: jira, dhisan.
baabba'sanaan: -ta: (maga, dhedig, keli) wax tirmay ahaan, burbursanaan. Meel dagaal ka dhacay baaba'sanaanta ayaa lagu gartaa.
baabbi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) daal iyo diihaal qofku aanu si quman isku taagi karin. Dh: dalanbaabbi.
baabbi'i: (fal) wax jira tirtir oo wax masaxan ka dhig. Qoraalku waa foolxun yahaye baabi'i, Dh: tirtir, masax.
baabbi'id: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) tirtirmid oo wax masaxmay ahaan. Xinnuhu intuu gacanta ku dhegayo baabi'idda ka ilaali. Dh: masaxmid.
baabbul: -sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) timo ama dhogor badan oo halab ah. Aar baabul leh indhihiisa waa laga naxaa. Dh: shaash, halab, bulbul.
baabeyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka uu qofka turubka ciyaarayaa hayo labo baab oo sooc ah.
baabfur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) sixir iyo fal horey la isugu dhigay furiddii; sixir iyo baab hore, wax ku akhriyid oo burin. Baabfur iyo dabiib culimo loo yeedho, Eebbe waa bogsiin karaa, bukaan baaddil lagu baabay. Dh: sixirfur.
baabfurid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baab horey la isugu dhigay furid oo burin; fal ama sixir hore qof loogu qabtay rogid. Dh: sixirfurid
baabfuryo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) Quraan iyo dikri lagu aqriyo ruux la falay oo lagaga rogo sixirka si looga buriyo. Allebari iyo baabfuryo ha loo sameeyo bukaanka baaban. Dh: sixirfuryo.
baabid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) fal qofka ruuxiisa dhiba ku akhriyid; girigiri u samayn; sixir iyo wax xun u qabad. Baabiddu waa xaaraan. Dh: sixrid, baabis, qataarid, falid.
baabi'i: (fal) wax hore u jirey tirtir; cagta mari. Baabi'i raadka yaan la arkine. Dh: masax, tirtir.
baabi'id: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) tirtirmidda wax hore u jirey; wax jiray oo baaba' noqday. Dh: lumid, tirtirmid, masaxmid.
baabi'id -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) edebta iyo dhaqanka oo qof ka xumaada.
baabi'in: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax jiray tiriddi wax aan jirin ka dhigid. Baabi'inta ka daa reerka. Dh: tirtirid.
baabi'isasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax baaba'san ka dhigasho.
baabi'iso: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) walax yar oo waxa qoran lag tirtiro. Dh: masaxaad, goomad.
baabi'itaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) tirtirmitaanka wax jirey oo raadkiisa la waayey.
baabilo: -da: (magac, dheddig, keli) lafdhabarleyda, soo baxyo uu jidhku leeyahay oo u soo baxa dubdhuleedka, ku waas oo kordhiya halka ay isaga yimaadaan labo nudood.
baabiloomo: -da: (magac, dheddig, keli) soobax ku yaalla maqaarka sare ama xuubmalaaska, sida ilmasidaha dhexdiisa.
baabitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) fal ku akhriyid; sixir ku samayn. Baabitaanku waa xaaraan. Dh: sixritaan.
baabliin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) maro daaqad ah oo Soomaalidii hore shamiisyada iyo go'yaasha la huwado ka goosan jirtey. Bista baasha ka feedhoo, shaadh baabliinana qaado. Dh: baabulliin.
baabnaw: (fal) qof baaban ama la falay, ahaw Baabnaw adaa raba, weligaa ba beentee.
baabsad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) xoolo ay leedahay cid kali iska calaamadsasho. Baabsadka neef aad lahayni waa damac qaldan.
baabsasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baad cid kali leedahay iska suntasho oo kuwaaga ku biirsasho. Dh: duntasho.
baabsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) xoolo cid kale oo aanad lahayn oo aad kas ugu darsato kuwaaga. Baabsiga iyo boolida joojiya. Dh: boob, dhac.
baabul: -sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhogor badan oo isku cufan; timo badan oo lusha. Buhubuhadii laga teg iyo baabul kicintiiye. Dh: gas, duful, shaash, halab, daacuf, tuur, bulbul, yoofil, doofil.
baabulle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) magac ka mid ah magacda libaaxa. Baabullow baa, beledkeennii soo galay. Dh: shaashle, halable, aar.
baabuur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gaadiid ku socda afar walxood ama in ka badan oo ka samaysan bir iyo cinjir neef lagu afuufay kuna shaqeeyaa shidaal. Dh: gaadhi, gaari, tamaamuul.

baabuur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qalab jikada loo adeegsado. Dhagax si farshaxannimo loo qoray ama ka samaysan ama walax bir ah oo inta dhuxul lagu shido wax lagu dul kariyo. Distida baabuurka dul saar oo xeraadka innoo kari. Dh: birjiko, girgire, marakab, burjiko.
baac: -a: (magac, lab, keli) cabbirka dhererka labada gacmood oo midig iyo bidix u kala baxsan. Ceelkani waa saddex baac iyo badh.
baac -a: (magac, lab, keli) inta u dhaxaysa qoorta ama xabadka iyo gacan keli ah oo la furay.
baac -a: (magac, lab, keli) luqunta geela. Hareeriga ka baxay foocyadey baaca gelisaaye. Dh: luqun, qoor.
baacdheer: -ta: (magacwadeer) ceelasha birqodyada ah ee dhaadheer ee waadaanta iyo dawliska lagaga cabbo. Ceelku waa baacdheer oo ciyaar laguma shubo. Dh: matan.
baaci: (fal) baac ku cabbir; gacmaha ku qiyaas. Dh: qiyaas.
baaci: (fal) dad ama xawayaan eryo; xoog u eryo oo ha ka hadhin; ku dabadhac. Libaaxii waa la baaciyey. Dh: gaaci, buubi.
baaci: (fal) kor ugu qaad gacmaha ilaa inta aad iska sarraysiin karto; sare u qaad; madaxaaga dusha ka mari oo dallac. Dh: bidh; bil.
baacid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax inta sare loo qaado halka ugu sarraysa ee ay gaadhi karaan la gaadhsiiyo. Baacid dheeraa ninkani.
baacin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baac ku cabbirid; gacmaha oo la kala baxshay, wax dhererkii ku qiyaasid.
baacin -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax inta sare loo qaado, lagu simo halka ugu sarraysa ee ay gacmuhu gaadhi karaan.
baacitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) kor u qaaditaan labada gacmood wax lagu qaado oo madaxa kor loo dhaafiyo.
baacmushtar: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) shaqo ganacsi oo gasha mood, nool iyo aqoon ba. Dh: ganacsi, baayacmushtar, tijaarad.
baacsad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ku dabadhicid iyo eryasho. Ciidan guulaystay ayaa baacsad sameeya.
baacsan: (tilmaame) fidsan oo wax la ballaadhiyay ah. Gogol baacsan ayaan ku fadhiistay. Dh: fidsan, goglan. Li: duuban.
baacsan: (tilmaame) wax la dhereriyey ahaan. Dawlisku wuu baacsan yahaye, berri geela ku soo waraabiya. Dh: qiyaasan, cabbiran.
baacsanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax la fidiyay oo ballaadhsan ahaan. Dh: goglanaan, fidsanaan. Li: duubnaan.
baacsanaan -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax baac lagu qiyaasay ahaan.
baacsanaansho: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) wax la fidiyay oo ballaadhsan ahaansho. Dh: baacsanaan.
baacsanaansho -ha: (magac, lab, keli) wax baac lagu cabbiray ahaansho.
baacsasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ballaadhsiga wax duubnaa oo la kala bixiyo ama la fidiyo.
baacsasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, sil aad ah u caydhsasho oo eryasho. Baacsashada sidii goroyo banjoogtaan, bahallada ka cararaaye. Dh: caydhsasho, eryasho.
baacsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax duubnaa ama laabnaa, fidsasho oo ballaadhsasho. Dh: ballaadhsi, fidsi.
baacsi -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cid kale, aad u eryasho oo caydhsi.
baacso: (fal) gogol iyo wixii la mid ah oo duubnaa, fidso oo ballaadhso. Furaashka baacso oo ku seexo. Dh: goglo, fidso.
baacso: (fal) eryo oo ku daba dhac. Baacso tuugga oo soo qabo. Dh: caydhso, eryo.
baacug: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) caano la fadhiisiyey: caano la gadhoodhiyay oo la adkeeyey, Baacug baan saaka ku soo quraacday. Dh: farmaajo, furumaaj, gadhoodh. Li: dhay.
baacug -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dhasha yaryar oo aan weli uus yeelan; xoolaha yaryar ee aan weli caano mooyee calooshooda wax kale gelin. Naylaha mareegta ku jiraa, waa baacug aan ababin.
baacug -ga: (magac, lab, keli) caloosha aan weli uus yeelan oo aan caano mooyee wax kale gelin. Maqal baacug madhan baa reerka ku hadhay oo dhulku waa abaar.
baad: (fal) dalkii lagugu yaqaannay ama dadkaagii in badan ka raag oo ka maqnaw.
baad -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolo si xaqdarro ah qof lagaga qaato; xoolo si gardarro iyo kibir ah cid lagaga muquunsado. Fircoon riciyaddiisa ayuu baad ka qaadi jiray.

baad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) nooluhu waxay quutaan oo aan biyo ahayn. Diirta baadka idlaysiyo, waxaad tahay bullaroora aan da'ayn. Dhul abaar ah oo aan baad iyo biyo toona lahayn baan soo arkay. Dh: cunto, calaf, kimis, daaq.
baad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) labada garab ee noolaha duula ama diyaaradaha midkood. Shimbiri baad bay ku duushaa. Wa: baadad.
baad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baalka isha; timaha isha ku xeeran middood. Baad baa isha igaga dhacay. Dh: baal.
baada: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolo dadkii lahaa ka lumay oo cid kale la socda. Dh: baadi.
baadad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciyaarta turubka oo la ka la badin waayo, dabadeed inta la xidho la ka la helo marka kaa xiga.
baaddil: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax kaste oo aan daw ahayn ama qaldan.
baaddilnimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax qaldan ahaan; wax aan sharci ku salaysnayn ahaan.
baaddiye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) deegaanka reer guuraaga ee nolosha aan qaab magaalo ku salaysnayan.
baaderi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) ninka kanisadda Kiristaanka ugu sarreeya. Dh: baadari, kuhaan, baadderi.
baadh: (fal) raadi wax ka maqan ama ka dahsoon. Qaamuuska ka baadh macnaha ereyga. Dh: raadi, baar, ji.
baadh -ka: (magac, lab, keli) afarta haad ee turubku leeyahay mid ka mid ah. Dh: baar.
baadhad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baadhashada la baadho qof si gardarro ah.
baadhan: (tilmaame) wax ama meel la baadhay oo gacanta la mariyey.
baadhasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof ama meel, hanti si sharcidarro ah kaga qaadasho.
baadhasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax maqan ama daahan, doondoonasho.
baadhasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) galgalashada ama doondoonashada fadhiga wanaagsan ee gaar ahaan geela. Baadhashada badanaa ma dhuug baa cunaya hasha!
baadhe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof kormeere sare ah oo hawlo dabagal ah ku jira, dabadeedna hawshaa xog ka soo gudbiya. Baadhe ayaa khasnadda dawlladda loo diray.
baadhid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax qarsoon raadintii, si runtiisa loo gaadho ama xog badan looga ogaado. Baadhid badan ka dib, waxa la ogaaday in uu Islaamku Madiina horteed Geeska Afrika soo gaadhay. Dh: baarid, raadin, ji, fatishid, baadhis.
baadhis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baadigoobidda wax maqan oo la tebayo.
baadhis -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid ka mid ah xiddigaha Soomaalidu ka awaalasheegaan. Waxay isgarab yihiin ururka iyo agaallicaanoodka. Xiddigtii baadhis caaway soo baxday.
baadhitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax dahsoon raadintii si runtiisa loo gaadho ama xog badan looga ogaado.
baadho: (fal) wax kaa qarsoon doondoono; wax kaa dahsoon raadso. Buugga aad raadinayso ka baadho maktabadda.
baadho: (fal) gelgelin ku galgalo; isrogrog adiga oo dhinacyada kolba mid u jiifsanaya. Awrkii dhaanka laga furay gelgelintuu baadhanayaa.
baadi: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolo ama wax kale lumay oo laga yaabo inay cid kale la socdaan. Baadi nimaan lahayn bay ag joogtaa. Nin waliba sidii baadi geel, naga banjoogowye. Dh: baada.
baadibariin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baadida oo ciddii lahayd la gaadhsiiyo; xoolo ciddii lahayd ka lumay oo la bariiyo oo la ilaaliyo inta dadkii lahaa u imanayaan. Baadibariin baa dadkeenna lagu yagaannaa.
baadibooliye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka baadida xoolihiisa soo raacda ba'sada ee xalaalaysta
baadicarar: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baydadka iyo qaloodka neefka baadida ah oo cidda uu soo raacay la qabsan waaya.
baadid: -da: (mayac, dhedig, keli) cela magnaan dheeraata. Scadid ku kala raugnays helmaan, baro wada galeyna. Dh: baaris, raagid, dachid, dibloed
baadid -da: (maqac, dhedig, kel.) Laydhitaanka iyo leexashada dhiuc la maro. Kobta adhiga becaubu degay kor uga baadaye
baadidoon: (fal) raadi baadi kaa maqan. Orod oo baadido awrkii Candaawe. Dh: raadraac, raad, raadcee, doon
baadidoon -ka: magar, lab, kuli) raadcada xoolo maqan oo loo malaynayo inay cid kale raaceen. Dh: baadigoob, razdca, raadin.
baadidoonid: -da: (magas, dedig, keli raadco u bixid, wax hallaabay heliddii u ambabixi Raggi xalay budidooniddii averka ayay ku maqneayren.
baadifad: -da: (magar, dhedig, kell) qofka baadida hela abaalgudka la siiyo. Dh: abaalmarin.
baadigef: baadigef -ka (magac, lab, keli) baadiddoon adag oo had ba sees laga maro baadidii oo lagu dhibaatoodo: baadi doondoon keegii Lagu guulcarraystay. Baadigef ayaa igu dhacay.
baadigefid: da: (maga, dhedig, keli) meesha ay baadidu joogto meel aan ahayn ka raadis.
baadigoobid: -da: (magar, dhedig, keli raadinta xoolo ama wax kale xc lamay. Dh: baadiddoonid, baadimadis, baadigoobis.
baadigoobis: -ta: (magac, ledig. keli) wax lumay doondoonid oo kolba moel ka raadis. Dh: raadin, raadcayn.
baadihallayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale khatal.doc jidka ka lamin.
baadil: -ka: (magcc, lab, keli) laabta dadka iyo shafka hore. Baadilka ayuu kubadda ku si qaatay, daladced na wau sii dhaliyay Dl: shafka, laabta, hayd, xabac.

baadil -ka: imagoc, lab, kelil wax aa: xaq abava, ka baxsan xeerka ama ka duwan sidi toosnayd. Waa duni xadgudubtoo, xaqa baadil qariyoo la is wada xaqirayee! Dh: baadul, dulmi, gardarro, jiddarro, xaqdarro. Li: xaq.
baadila: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xilliyada qaarkood, xaalad ay baddu noqoto oo caariga iyo buuxitaanku dheeraadaan oo ay dhawr maalmood socdaan. Baddu maalmahan waa baadila. Dh: caari, habso.
baadino: (tilmaame) bad deggan; bad fadhida oo aan kacsanayn. Baadino ayay ahayd baddu maanta.
baadis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) kala maqnaanshaha muddo dheer. Anna baadistaadaa, boholyow i gelisoo, naftaa kuu ba'aysee.
baadisooc: -a: (magac, lab, keli) calaamad lagu kala saaro xoolaha; summad xoolaha lagu dhigo si looga garto kuwa cid kale leedahay. Dh: astaan, summad.
baadisoocid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) calaamad iyo summad uu leeyahay ku garasho oo ku soo soocid.
baaditaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) kala maqnaansho daba dheeraaday. Baaditaan baan ku kala maqnqyn.
baadixafid: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ilaalinta xoolo aanad lahayn oo baadi kugu soo galay; ammaano xajinteed. Nin baadixafid badan baadidii ma baylahdo.
baadiyayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) luminta xoolo qof ilaalinayay. Sahal waa nin baadiyayn badan. Dh: lumin, fakin, hallayn, dayacid.
baadiyayn -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof reer magaal ahaa, baadiye ka dhigid; dhaqanka baadiyaha u yeelis. Dh: miyiyeyn.
baadiyayn -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale qaldid oo khatalid. Dh: lumin.
baadiyayn -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) jidka hagaagsan ee diintu tilmaantay ka leexin oo gaalnimo u horseedid. Li: hanuunin.
baadiyaysan: (tilmaame) mid hallawsan oo baadi ah. Dh: lunsan, hallawsan.
baadiyaysan: (tilmaame) jidka hanuunka ka leexsan oo jid shaydaan haysta. Ninka aan salad tukanin waa nin baadaiyaysan.
baadiyaysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid lumay ahaan. Dh: hallawsanaan.
baadiyaysnaansho: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) mid lumay oo jidkii saxda ahaa ka baydhay ahaansho. Dh: baadiyaysnaar..
baadiye: -ha: (magac, lab, kel) dhulka magaalada ka baxsan ee xoola dhaqatadu dego. Dh: miyi
baadiyee: (fal) xoolo cad ilaalinaysay lumi; wax aad baysay bacdi ka chig. Dh: baadiyec, lumi, faki, dayac, hallee.
baadiyee: (fal) qof, reer baadiye ka dhig. S wiilku soo adkaado baadiyee.
baadiyee: (fal) lumi oo daw qaldan mari baadi ha noqdee. Dh: baadihaller
baadiyee: (fal) dawga hanuunka ka leexi oo jidka shaydaanka mari.
baadiyeyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dariiqa xaqa ah ka leexin.
baadiyoobid: -da: (magac, dhecig. keli) wax baadi ah oo lunsan ahaansho.
baadiyoobid -da: (magac, chediq, keli, reer miyi noqosho, baadiye abaan.
baadiyow: (fal) 'xoolo' noqo haadi uo cid kale raac. Baraarkii labaa baadiyoobay Dh: lun, hallaw
baadiyow: (fal) baadiye noqo, reer miyi noco.
baadiyow: (fal) dawga hanuunka ka leexo; xaqa iyo caddaaladda ka leexo; dhaqanka iyo usluubta hallee. Dh: lun, hallaw. habaw
baadiyow -ga: (mogac, lab, keli) baadiye noqosho reer miyi iska dhigid ama ahaansho.
baadiyow -ga: (magac, lab, keli) xoolo la ilaalinayay on luna.
baadiyow -ga: (magac, lab, keli) iilashada qof ka baydha xaqa iyo caddaaladca: qof dhaqanka iyo asluubtu ka lumaan.
baaf: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) mid ka mid ah qalabka codka weyneeya, bahiyana. Baaf baa i dul yaalay oo waxba ma maqlayn, kolkaad ila hadlaysay.
baaf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) saxanka lagu dhaqo maryaha; saxniga dharka lagu maydho. Dh: tashti, saxni, sixni, saxan.
baafi: (fal) xoolo ama wax kale oo lumay raadi. Db: yaboohi, docndoon, dayday, cayniqabo, yaahi.
baafin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax Jumay raadintii. Baafin baa baadi lagu helaa. Dh: yabcohin.
baag: -ta: (magac, dhedig, kel:) calaamade ku faafa oogada qofka oo cadcad oo diirka sare hoola. Baag baa qoorta wiilka ka soo baxday. Dh: cambaar
baaga: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gubbaha iyo baadda cid kaa awood badan cabsi loo siiyo.
baagamuuddanimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) shaqo, iyo merehrad waayitaan.
baagamuuddayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) shaqo iyo meherad la'aan ku joogid. Dh: faaltuuyeyn.
baagamuuddee: (fal) shaqo la'aan ku joog; meherad waa; faaltuunimo ku joog. Dh: baagamuuddee.
baagamuuddo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dad ama ruux aan meherad haysanin ama shaqaynin; dad camal iyo shaqo aan lahayn. Baagamuuddada, bannaannada tuban, yaan la baal marin.
baaggiye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) daqiiq la qooyay oo inta la kuuskuuso saliid lagu dubo. Waxa lagu dhuuqaa basbaas qooshan.
baah: (fal) dhul badan gaadh; is ballaadhi oo meelo hor leh gaadh. Geelii wuu baahay. Dh: faaf. baahid
baah -a: (magac, lab, keli) dhul badan gaadhid; meelo aanu hore u jirin gaadhid. Dh: baahis.
baaha: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax la'aan; hayn la'aan. Dh: baahi.
baahabeel: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gaajo iyo baahi jirtay tirid; dhergid oo haqabbeelid.
baahan: (tilmaame) qof ama shey wax baahi u qaba sida dhuuni, dhar, caafimaad ama wax kale. Waan baahanahay bakhti looma cuno.
baahane: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof aan waxba haysan. Sadaqada baahanaha siiya. Dh: caydh.
baahane -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof baryo badan oo mar walba weydiin u taagan.
baahasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax kaa maqan rabtid. Baahasho booli looma qaato.
baahawadaag: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dad dano fara badan ka dhexeeyaan oo istaageersada.
baahay: (fal) qaadhaan qof u ururi; u soo dhawrtee; dadka u soo dhexmar: baaha u soo gur. Dh: baahee.
baahayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof sabool ah ama gacan madhan, gargaar u soo ururin. Dh: qaadhaamid, jiscin.
baahaysasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baaho iyo gargaar urursasho.
baahi: (fal) dhul badan gaadhsii oo ku ballaadhi: meel ku kala bixi. Baahi warka bulshadu ha wada maqashee. Dh: faafi, fidi, firdhi. Li: ururi, koob.
baahi -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax la'aan; hayn iyo jeeb xumo. Baryo iyo baahi badan ba waa la isku nacaa. Dh: baaha.
baahi -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dareenka rabitaan ama doonitaan ee wax ama qof loo hayo. Baahidaan kuu qabo, babarkaad iga jirtaan, soo bildhaasadaa.
baahibeel: (fal) ka kaaftoon baahidii qof ama wax aad u qabtay.
baahibeel -ka: (magac, lab, keli) beelista gaajo ama xaajo kale oo la qabo; baahi laga haqabbeelo. Dh: baahabeel.
baahibeelid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baahi wax ama qof loo qabay oo laga kaaftoomo. Dh: haqab-beelid.
baahid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kala ballaadhasho gaadhista meelo aan hore loo gaadhin. Ururiya cawska oo baahidda ka ilaaliya. Dh: faafid, firdhid. Li: ururid.
baahid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) habsocodka ilayska iyo hirarka makanikada ama birlab-danabeedka. Baahidda iftiinku way sii ballaadhataa kolba kolka ay meesha ifaysa ka sii fogaato.
baahila: magac loo baxsho gabadh la filayo inay noqoto mid aan baahan oo hodan ah.
baahillaawe: midka aan wax baahi ah qabin; ka aan wax ba u baahnayn. Dh: Alle, Ilaah, Ilaahey, Eebbe, Rabbi.
baahin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) fidinta wax lagu faafiyo meel aanu hore u gaadhsiisnayn. Dh: fidin, firdhin.
baahis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ballaadhashada. iyo faafidda wax meel keli ah ku kaabnaa.
baahitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) faaafitaanka war ama wax kale. Dh: fiditaan.
baahitir: (fal) qof ka bi'i baahi haysa; sii waxa uu u baahan yahay.
baahitir -ka: (magac, lab, keli) sahay ama sed kale oo qof baahan loo fidiyo; gargaar qof ama koox la siiyo. Baahitir bay martidu innaga codsatay.
baahitirid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) shey, qof ama koox wax tebaysa oo laga bi'iyo tabashada iyo baahida wax u haysa.
baahiwadaag: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dad baahi ka dhexayso oo wax mid ah wada tabanaya.
baahiye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof ama qalab war ama wax kale baahiya oo dhul badan gaadhsiiya.
baahnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qabitaanka baahida ama haqab.
baahnaanshiiyo: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) xaaladda baahnaanta ee lagu jiro.
baahnaw: (fal) ahaw ruux baahi wax u qaba; qof aan weli helin rabitaankiisa ahaw. Waan baahanahay bakhti loo ma cuno.
baahni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xaaladda baahida lafteeda; doonista wax baahi weyni loo qabo.
baahniin: baahniin -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ku baahitaanka dhul badan; ku fiditaanka meel aanu hore u gaadhin.
baaho: (fal) yeelo rabitaanka wax ama qof; baahi u qab wax, sida cunto, caafimaad cilmi ama qof.

baaho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolaha gargaar ahaan reeraha ama dadka looga soo ururiyo; xoolo lagu bixiyo magta ama qof baahan loo guro. Baaho ayaan u soo ururinnay dadkii socotada ahaa. Dh: xoolaggooyo, qaadhaan.
baaho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) guddi qaybaha ay xaajadu khusayso oo dhan ka kooban oo ay xeer-beegti meel u dirto.
baahsan: (tilmaame) aad u baahay oo faafay; dhul badan gaadhay. Dh: fidsan, firidhsan.
baahsanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhul badan gaadhsiisnaan. Baahsanaan iyo baylah ba barta ka eega. Baahsanaadka bahalkaa ku laaya xoolaha. Dh: faafsanaan, firirsanaan, fidsanaan.
baahsanaansho: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) wax baahsan oo kala firidhsan ahaansho. Wax aan nidaam lahayn waxad ku garan baahsanaashaha. Li: urursanaan, habaysanaan.
baahsanaw: (fal) mid aan habaysnayn ahaw; mid baahsan ahaw. Baahsanaw adaa baylahdiyo doortay baabba'a e.
baahsane: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof aan wax u urursanayn oo hawlihiisa iniba meel ku firidhsan tahay. Baahsane inta ka ba'aysaa badan.
baahsani: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) faafitaanka dhul badan wax gaadhaan.
baahsani -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kala qaabdarro iyo daadsanaan.
baaji: (fal) wax dhici lahaa, maaro u hel; dib u dhig. Martida waa la casuumaye, safarka ha laga baajiyo. Dh: nagee, jooji.
baaji: (fal) jebi ballan xidhnaa. Ballantiyo axdiga baajiyay beenta igu waasho.
baaji -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kala jeedista labada gees ee lo'da qaarkeed. Saca baajida leh hardida kuma fiicna.
baajin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dhici lahaa, maaro u helid oo joojin ama dib u dhigid. Dh: nageyn, joojin.
baajin -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ballan in la qabto la sugayay oo laga baaqsado. Beenaale ballan baajis badanaa.
baajisan: (tilmaame) wax ka baaqday inuu dhaco ama maaro loo helay.
baakad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) buqshad waraaq ama kartoon ka samaysan oo afar gees oo iska soo horjeeda leh oo alaabaha lagu moodhgareeyo sida qafiska sigaarka. Dh: baakidh, baakeed, buqshad, baako, baakir.
baakiri: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dameerta la rarto. Baakiri heeryaysan, biyahaan ku soo dhaansan.
baal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cudur xummad badan oo dadka ku dhaca.
baal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) laan ka mid ah laamaha dhogorta leh ee baadka wixii duula. Baal gorayo ayuu Cali madaxa gashaday. Wa: baalal.
baal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) suqusha iyo saxarka ka soo hadha hadhuudhka marka la tumo ama la shuqlo. Baalka ka reeba hadhuudhka. Dh: buunshi, buushi, buunsha, weega.
baal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) waraaqaha kitaabku ka kooban yahay midkood. Baalka kitaabka ha qoynin Dh: xaashi. Wa: baalal.
baal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) tin ka mid ah kuwa ka baxa isha hareerteeda. Baal baa isha igaga dhacay.
baal -sha: (magac, lab, keli) goob dhinac kaa xigta. Waar ha i jiidhine, baal iga mar. Dh: dhinac, gees, fay, doc, barbar. Wa: baallo.
baalallee: (fal) ugu horree kolka wax la qabanaay. Dabbaasha noo baalalee. Dh: horree, daar.
baalalley: -da: (magacwadareed) cayayaanka duula jaad ka mid ah oo ka dhasha roobka.
baalalley: (ereycodeed) carruurtu tidhaahdo marka ay biyaha ku ciyaarayaan, iyaga oo uga jeeda saydhista biyaha. Biyo batalaq baalalley.
baalash: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhaashiga midabka leh ee kabaha la mariyo si bilicdooda loo muujiyo
baalashayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) kabaha oo dhaashi midabaysan la mariyo oo lagu qurxiyo.
baalashee: (fal) mari kabaha baalash ama dhaashi midabaysan.
baalashle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) wiilka baalashka kabaha mariya. Wa: baalashleyaal.
baalaxoofto: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hanjabaad aan run ahayn; cagajuglayn been ah, gooddiyid aan dhab ahayn. Dh:goolaaftan, jiirfeed.
ba'alayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ku celcelinta ereyga 'ba'a' laftirkiisa. Ba'alaynta balaayaa ka danbaysa.
baalcad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) middi aad u af badan; middi xiiraysa waxay taabato.
baalcad: (tilmaame) 'neef' dhinacyadiisa midi cadyahay. Sicii baalcad wuu dhalay
baaldaaq: -a: (magac, lab, keli) neef gooni xoolaha kale uga daaga. Neefka baaldaaga ahi waraabuu u halis yahay. Dh: goonidaaq, goonijoog, feedhjoog, adoole, manoy, sagandaaq, muudaa, keliginoole, xaalwaa.
baaldacar: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baalka dacartu bixiso ee dhabaqa yeesha; qaybta bixisa ubaxa iyo iniinta ee geedka dacarta. Dh: baaldacareed.
baaldhiig: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) baalasha buka ee haadka. Baaldhiigga waa laga rifaa haadka, haddii uu cudur ku faafo. Dh: tinmood.
baaldi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) weel macdan ama caag ka samaysan oo biyaha la darsado ama lagu qaato. Baaldi biyo ah soo dar. Dh: sakayl. Wa: baaldiyo.
baalfallaadh: -a: (magac, lab, keli) shimbir calool cad dhabarkana madaw iyo buluug ah oo baadad dhaadheer oo falladh u eg iyo dabo fantaxle leh oo xiiliba meel u hayaanta oo kooxkoox u duula.
baalgarab: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) garabka kalluunka baal ka baxa oo ka saacida dabbaasha. Baalgarabka gabo kalluunka. Dh: seeb. Wa: baalgarabyo.
baalgorayo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baalasha gorayada mid ka mid ah ee mamayuuxsan. Baalgoroyo waa tuu gashaday geesigaan dhalaye.
baalgoroyayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) u labo ruux oo looltamaya, dagallaamaya soo dhexgelid oo labada mid u hoosaasin ama u hoodaadin; labo qof oo ishaysa, midkood si dadban ugu hiilin; u mijin qabasho.
baali: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof dumar ah oo aan nadaafadda iyo miigganaan badan lahayn. Baali dumar, baradeeda eedday. Dh: basari, goonbaar. Li: gaari, dhabeel.
baali: (tilmaame) weel aan cugnayn. Dhiil baali ah baad caanaha ku shubtay.
baali: (tilmaame) shey la isticmaalay oo gaboobay sida dhar; walax aan cusbayn.
baalid: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) walax duug ah. Baalid dharku wuxuu noqdaa markaan, boodhka laga maydhin.
baalid -ka: (magac, lab, keli) weel aan bilo waxba lagu shuban ama lagu ridan. Baalid gaawuhu wuu ka bixi markuu, geelo wada irmaanaado.
baalidid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) curinta gabayga oo laga raago ama laga maago.
baalidid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) weel aan bilo waxba lagu shuban ama lagu ridan ahaan.
baaliyoobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax gaboobay oo hun ah noqosho. Dh: duugoobid, humoobid.
baaliyow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) noqoshada wax baali ah. Baaliyowga ka dhawro dharkaaga.
baaliyow: (fal) noqo wax gaboobay. Haddaad baaliyowda na, birtaney kuma daayo. Dh: duugow.
baalkarrid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadhuudh la tumay oo baalka laga saaray ama laga riday. Dh: buunshabixid.
baalkarridid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadhuudh tumid oo gal ka saarid ama gal ka ridid.
baalkutaabay: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cayayaan leh baadad aad midabaysan oo u qurux badan. Waxa ay jeceshahay ubaxa iyo doogga dushiisa oo ay ku fadhiisataa. Dh: balambaallis.
baallacad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) walax bir ah oo hub ahaan loo isticmaalo. Bir la afeeyay oo uu soofuhu labada dhinac caddeeyay ama hillaacaysa. Dh: abley, toorri, toorrey.
baallaybaroor: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cayayaan duula oo balambaallista la jaad ah, inuu iskii hawada isku taago na awood u leh. Gaar ahaan, waxaa u ku nolyahay meelaha biyaha leh. Dh: boollibarooro.
baallayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhinac jirid; doc xigid. Baallaynta iga daayoo dhexda soo joogso.
baalle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) baal iyo baad uu ku duulo leh. Baalleh barbar walba wuu u duulaa.
baalle -ha: (magac, lab, keli) nin baal madaxiisa ka ka taagan yahay oo rag uu laayay ku baashaday. Baalle biri qaadday booyini ma soo celiso. Dh: geesi. Li: fule.
baalle -ha: (magac, lab, keli) tiirka korontada ee fiilooyinka lagu xidho.
baalle: naanays loo baxsho wiil orodka dheereeya si uu leeyahay baal shimbireed.
baallee: (fal) dhinac ama fay xig: dhinac mar ama ugu shishee. Baallee adigu, Buux na bartanka ha yimaaddo. Dh: koonee.
baalleeco: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dhinac u qallooca.
baalley: -da: (magacwadareed) wixii baad ku duula oo dhan. Baalleyda duushaan, la dalxiisi doonaa. Dh: baadley.
baalley -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciyaardhaqameed caan ku ah gobolka Ceerigaabo iyo inta u dhow oo jiib iyo jaanba leh oo la isku maaweeliyo.
baallood: (fal) hareeraha day, baallahaaga eeg. Markaan baallooday baan buugga arkay
baallood -ka: (magac, lab, keli) daymo hareeraha ah. Anigaaba baalloonayee baarax baa dhacaye. Dh: jeelaalo, jalleeco, daymood.
baalsasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof kale oo cadaw ah, dilkiisa baal ku qaadasho oo ku faanid ama sharaf ku sheegasho.
baalshiig: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) baalasha haadka ku wooda buka oo laga rifo. Digaagga baalshiigga ka rif.
baaluq: (fal) qaangaadh noqo; xadka baaluqa gaadh. Inankaygii weynaa wuu baaluqay.
baaluq -a: (magac, lab, keli) qaangaadh noqosho; da'da la xisaabtanka. Dh: qaangaadh, qaangaar.
baaluqe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka baaluqay ee gaadha da'da xilqaadashada.
baaluqid: -da: (magac,dhedig, keli) waqtigii baaluqa gaadhid; da'dii xilqaadashada gaadhid.
baaluqnimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) mudakar ahaan. Cibaadada baaluqnimo ayaa loo shardiyaa. Dh: baaluqid, qaangaadhnimo.
baaluqsan: (tilmaame) qof gaadhay xilligii baaluqitaanka; qof qaangaadhay. Bildhaantiisa markaad eegto waa nin baaluqsan.
baaluqsanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ahaanshaha qof baaluqsan. Baaluqsanaani kama muuqato codkiisa.
baalxaaf: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) jaad warmaha ka mid ah oo aad u af weyn, si gaar ahna loo sameeyo. Baalxaafka waxa loo sitaa, baylah kaa magane.
baalxooftayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baalxoofto samayn oo hanjabaad; gooddi iyo cagajuglayn la imasho. Baalxooftaynta iska dhaaf oo bannaanka u soo bax
baalxooftee: (fal) cid kale u cagajuglee; isku taartaar oo u hanjab.
baambad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhuunta biyaha laga shubto; dhuun bir ama caag ah oo ay biyihu soo dhexmaraan. Waxay leedahay meel laga furo iyo meel laga xidho. Baambadda fur oo biyaha soo dhaami.
baamiye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) jaad khudradda ka mid ah. Sariibadda tag oo baamiye noo soo gad.
ba'an: -ta: (magac, dhedigi keli) mid ka mid ah labada goor ee faalka la dhigo: Ba'anta kolka la dhigayo, 'war xun sheeg' baa la yidhaa.
ba'an -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) hilib ama cunto dheef, dux, waxtar iyo nafaqo leh oo loo sameeyo qof nabar soo gaadhay jidhkiisa si loo soo kabo. Dh: buullo, xannaano.
ba'an: (tilmaame) xun oo aan fiicnayn. Ninkii garramayay hadal ba'an ma odhan. Dh: qaldan, xun. Li: fiican.
ba'an: (tilmaame) dhib badan; belo badan; loo taag waayey. Dh: daran.
ba'an: (tilmaame) aad u buka oo sankaraad ah. Odaygii wuu ba'an yahay. Li: ladan.
ba'anay: (fal) wax ba'an ka dhig; qof ama wax kale, ka dhig wax daran oo xun.
ba'anaysasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baasaysashada wax ama qof aanad u bogin. Ba'anaysashada maalmaha barkood iska daaya.
ba'anayso: (fal) baasayso wax ama qof oo nac. Ha ba'anaysan hadalka waaliddada.
ba'ane: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof ama xayawaan kale oo lab oo daran ama belo badan. Ba'anaha dhurwaa, baadiduu dilaa.
baan: (fal) la garran qof ama dad gar iyo dacwadi idin ka dhaxayso. Si wanaagsan u baan oo ha caytamin. Dh: garran, dacwi.
baan: (fal) baaq oo u yeedh. Soomaali khayr baan ugu baanayaa.
baan: (fal) caddee oo qeex. Eray kalana waw noqonayaa unug yar baan baanay
baan: (fal) hadal gooddi, faan iyo dhaar isugu jira dheh.
baan: (qurub) falkaabe ah oo ka kooban 'baa' iyo 'aan' oo la isku daray. Cali baan arkay. Buux baan bariidiyey. Dh: ayaan.
baan -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hey'ad lacagta maamusha, kaydisa oo ilaalisa. Dh: bangi.
baan -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) laba duul ama laba qof oo ay dacwad dhextaallo doodda dhexmarta. Arrinta bir ha ku galinee, baan ku gala. Dh: baane.
baan -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dheefta dheeraadka ah ee la siiyo qofku markuu cawarmo ama jabo ama taag darreeyo la siiyo. Dh: nafaqayn, buullayn, baanasho.
baanaa: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) nin baanaha aad u yaqaan oo geedfadhi ah. Dh: garyaqaan.
baanad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) bir yar oo biraha gaadhiga lagu furfuro. Waar baanad 14 ah i sii. Dh: kiyaawe.
baanad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) siinta nafaqo iyo wixii la mid ah. Baanad buu ku jiraa oo buul yar baa loo dhisay.
baanbay: -da: (magacwadareed) kooxda muusigga gaardiska ciidanka u qaabilsan. Baanbayda boolisku astaantiisa ayay tumayaan.
baandhay: (fal) isdhexgeli oo isku dardar turubka si haadadku isugu dhafmaan. Baandhay turubka oo qaybi. Dh: baandhee.
baandhay: (fal) baadhitaan is dabajoog ah ku samee; fatashaad ku suubbi. Dh: baadh, baandhee, fatash.
baandhayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) isku hagaajin iyo isku habaynta turubka.
baandhaysan: (tilmaame) turub is dhexgashan oo isku dhafan.
baandhaysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) turub is dhexgashan oo isku dhafan ahaan.
baandhaysnaw: (fal) ahaw wax baandhaysan oo is ku dhafan.
baandhee: (fal) turub isku laaq oo is dhex geli si aan loo kala naqaysan karin. Dh: baandhay.
baandheeye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka turubka baandheeya ama wax kale ba baadhbaadha.
baandho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) turubka is dhexgelintiisa si haadadku isugu dhafmaan.
baando: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) koox askar ah oo loo diray meel shaqaaqo jirto.
baanduul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) biyaha doonta soo gala, meesha godan ee ay isugu tagaan ama ay fadhiistaan. Dh: banduul.
baane: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) gar u faadhiisasho; arrin dhacday xeerkeeda iyo xalkeeda raadin. Baane ayaa bartan berri loo fadhiisan doonaa.
baane -ha: (magac, lab, keli) hadalka ay isweydaarsadaan labada loo kala qarqaadayo oo xujooyin iyo markhaatiyo ama dhaar wata si mid walliba gartiisa u xoogeeyo. Dh: garran
baaneyahan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qofka baanaha aqoonta u leh ee dadka is haysta ee gartu ka dhaxayso kala saara.
baangad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) bir soo yara xoodan ama xalleefsan sida safeexadda ka se xooggan oo shaagagga baabuurta lagu banjariyo.
baani: (fal) dhuuni dux iyo waxtar leh sii. Baani bukaanka.
baani -ga: (magac, lab, keli) baadhis aan tudhaale lehayn. Boolisku baani bay nagu sameeyeen. Dh: degaanduug, faanbi.
baanid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka doodidda dacwad idin dhextaal adiga iyo cid kale.
baanin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) siinta cunto nafaqo leh, si qofku uga kabto bugtaan iyo dhaawac soo gaadhay. Baanin buu ku jiraa weli bukaanku.
baanis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale la dacwin. Baanis waagii beryaba beerku nagu caddaa.
baanise: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) hadal iyo dood meel fagaara ah laga yidhaahdo. Baanise badan beerkaa kugu daala. Dh: khudbad, garta, dacwad.
baanitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cid kale, la garramid.
baaniyaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qayb ka mid ah Hindida.
baaniye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka cid bukaan ah baxnaaniya.
baanji: (fal) baadhitaan iyo fatashaad ku samee; wax ka dhex raadi. Qorqode intuu aqalka baanjiyuu bilista daaliyaa. Dh: baadh, baar, baandhee.
baanji -ga: (magac, lab, keli) faandigid si xeeldheeri ah wax loo baadho oo meel walba faraha la geliyo. Dh: faandig.
baanji -ga: -(magac, lab, keli) cid kale, wax dux leh ku baanasho.
baanjiyid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) faandigid oo aad wax u doondoonid. Dh: doondoonid, raadin.
baankariya: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qanjidh ku ladhan marrinka dheefshiidka ee ku meelaysan caloosha agteeda. Wuxuu soo saaraa hormoonka insuliinta. Dh: beeryar.
baano: (fal) sii cunto nafaqo leh sida hilib iyo wixii la mid ah; tadaawi oo qof bukaan ah nafaqee. Dh: buullee, xannaanee, baxnaani.
baansad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qof buka, dhakhtar, wadaad ama cid kale oo wax dawaysa u geysasho. Dh: baanasho.
baansasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baan ku raysasho. Baansashadu bukaankan way ka muugataa.
baansasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof buka, dhakhtar, wadaad ama cid kale oo wax dawaysa u geysasho. Dh: baansad, baansi.
baansii: (fal) labo ama in ka badan oo ay dacwo dhex taal, u garqaad oo baanahooga ka dhegeyso Dh: garransii.
baansiin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dad khilaaf dhex yaal wada haladsiin. Dh: garransiin.
baanso: (fal) qof xidhiidh inniga dhexeeyo oo wax qaba adu iskaa iskaga baano oo daawayso. Dh: daawayso, dabiibo.
baantookh: -a: (magac, lab, keli) hadal badan oo aan macno iyo milgo midna lahayn. Dh: buuq.
baantookhid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadal aan macno lahayn ku hadaaqid. Dh: buuqid.
baantow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dibi doolaalada yaqaan; dibi lo'diisa iyo lo'yawga kale isugu mid yihiin. Dh: maalooti.
baaq: (fal) u baaq - cid kale cod dheer oo ujeeddo gaar ah sida u jeedi. Adduunyada dhammaanteed, ugu baaqnay taladii.
baaq -a: (magac, lab, keli) hadal kooban oo ujeeddo wata oo cid ku aaddan.
baaq -a: (magac, lab, keli) afgarasho ay samaystaan ciidamo ilaashanaya sirtooda. Waa hadal, qoral ama wax kale oo maldahan oo uu ciidan isku afgarto. Baaq baa ciidankii kale loo diray.
baaq -a: (magac, lab, keli) dhawaaq dheer oo ay dad kooxkoox u socdaa isugu baaqaan xilliyada geeddiga ama kolka la kala lumo ama xoola lumay la soo helo. Dh: uubato, lallab.
baaqad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax la filayey in uu dhaco ama uu yimaaddo oo waqtigii la sugayey dhici waayey ama ka dibdhaca. Dh: baaqasho, oolid.
baaqasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax daba mara oo ka dibdhaca waqtigii lagu waday in uu dhaco ama uu yimaaddo. Dh: dibudhac, dibdhac.
baaqbaaq: (fal) falitaan danbe oo dulmar ah ku samee beer baxday oo dheelli ah.
baaqbaaq -a: (magac, lab, keli) beer soo baxday oo dheelli ah falitaan danbe u samayn. Beertan baaqbaaq uma baahna.
baaqbaaqid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baaqbaaq ku samayn. Baagbaaqidda beerta, Beylow dibigiiyow, berri baa lagaa sugi. Dh: baaqbaaqis.
baaqbaaqitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baaqbaaqis ku suubbin beer.
baaqe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) kalluun yar oo isaga oo saliidaysan la qasaacadeeyo oo la jecel yahay. Dh: huduf, saardiin.
baaqi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) inta ka soo hadha wax la cunay ama la iibsaday ama la isticmaalay. Inta baaqu badan iyo baaqiqaa hadhi. Dh: hadhaa, hanbo.
baaqid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) jeedinta codsi ku baaqul wajahan meel ama cid gaar ah oo ujeeddo leh.
baaqimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hal geel oo caano yar. Hadday baatir geel kuu dhashoo, baaqimo noqoto, bilaash baa lagu baxshaa. Dh: badho, gabno, hooto. Li: ayro, deeqa, haldoor.
baaqis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, baaq u jeedin. Dh: baaqid.
baaqitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cid kale, u yeedhid ama codsi u jeedin.
baaqo: (fal) arrin ama talo lagu ballansanaa ka magnaw ama ka dibdhac.
baaqo: (fal) ka baaqo - ha iman meel ama madal lagaa filayey. Ha ka baagan shirka berrito. Dh: maqnaw
baaqsad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ka baaqsad - ka maqnaansho. Talo aan kaa maarmayn ka baaqsadkeedu ma fiicna.
baaqsasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka baaqsasho - gudasha la'aanta hawl aad qaban lahayd ama meel aad tegi lahayd.
baaqsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) ka baaqsi - wax la qaban lahaa ama meel iyo madal ka maqnaansho.
baaqsi -ga: (magac, lab, keli) neef xilligii uu rimi lahaa tebiyay oo aan rimin. Dh: tebis. Li: rimay.
baaqso: (fal) ka baaqso - ka maqnaw meel ama hawl aad qaban lahayd. Adigaa ka baaqsaday inaad barada dhawrtaaye.
baaqul: (fal) wax aan wanaagsanayn ka dhig; ufuuf ka dhig; biir ka yeel. Baaqullaysay hadalkee, ma been baa gabadhyahay, ballantii aan kula galay. Dh: uri, qadhmuunee, xumay, xumee.
baaqulayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadal la islaha xumayn; cid kale aflegaadayn.
baaqulhadal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadalxumo; afxumo. Dh: qadaf, aflagaaddo, deelqaaf, afxumo.
baaquli: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) weel godan oo lagu rito cuntada. Dh: maddeebad, maddiibad, qaafiri, xeedho.
baaqulle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ur qarmuun oo ceelasha biyahoodu yeeshaan.
baar: (fal) wax dahsoon ama aan la ogayn, doondoon. Dh: baadh.

baar: magac loo baxsho gabadh qurux iyo dhalaalba isku darsatay oo loogu magacdaray caleenta qoyan ama jilicsan ee geedka xilliga ay cusub tahay, waxa kale oo loo bixiyaa gabadh quruxdeeda uu dherer weheliyo.
baar -ka: (magac, lab, keli) curdinka sare ee geedka. Bardihii ku yiil isha Baydhabo, intuu gun iyo baar baxay, caleemuhu ballaadheen, baxarsaaf la moodyey. Dh: curub, laanyalax, yurub Li: jirrid.

baar -ka: (magac, lab, keli) geed caleen balballaadhan leh oo u dhalan eg yahay timirta. Waa geed dhala midho buurbuuran oo qoonne layiraahdo ay caruurta yaryar na cunaan. Dh: geedqoonne, geedbaar, bahaash.
baar -ka: (magac, lab, keli) maqaaxi yar oo buunka, khamrada iyo wixii la mid ah laga cabbo.
baar -ka: (magac, lab, keli) saynta iyo dhogorta ka baxda kuruska geela, ama faraska giirkiisa. Baarka ayaan ka jaray kuruskii awrka.

baar -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) geedgaab xashaashuqa ka mid ah oo ka baxa carisyada caleentiisuna bal balaadhan tahay. Waa geed xilli roobaadka soo baxa oo inta caleentiisa la maleego laga dhaliyo dhaacaan madow oo boogaha lagu dhayo. Burdad ubaxa baar iyo uneexo, bagas ku fuuraaga.
baaraabarakow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) khammaarid lacag loo huro wax aanad sii garanayn oo aad ku nasiibsato heliddii iyo waayid labadaba.
baaraan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax walba intiisa sare. Baaraanka qaado, laakiin badhka kale anigaa leh.
baaraandeg: (fal) ka baaraandeg - wax aad rabto qabashadiisa ka fiirso; ha ku degdegine sal iyo baarba hubi. Dhismaha hudheelka hortii, ka baraandeg kharashka ku bixi doona. Dh: hubso.

baaraandeg -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax aad looga fiirsado; wax aad u hubsasho; si qotodheer u dhuuxid. Arrintani baaraandeg bay ku habboon tahay. Dh: hubsasho, lafagur, gungaadh, axadhid, bogasho, bislayn, fiirsasho, xaqiijin.
baaraandegid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hubsasho qotodheer oo dhan xun iyo dhan fiicanba la fiiriyo, inta aan hawsha lagu dhaqaaqin. Baaraandegid la'aan talo kuma barbaarto.
baaraandegitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baaraandegidda lafteeda iyo hoos u eegitaanka badan ee hawl la qabanayo.
baarac: (tilmaame) qof da' yar oo dhan waliba buuxa.
baaracad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gabadh yar oo aan baaluqin; gabadh yar oo aan weli la xalaalayn.
baarad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax dahsoon ama aan la ogeyn, raadsasho. Dh: baadhad.
baarasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax kaa maqan ama kaa qarsoon raadsasho; iskaa u baadhasho ku samayn. Dh: baadhasho.
baarasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) galgalashada geela iyo faadhumaysigiisa.
baarashuud: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dallad, maro ama wax la mid ah ka samaysan oo cirka diyaaradaha lagaga soo boodo. Dh: baalashuud.
baarax: -a: (magac, lab, keli) wax kasta oo waafi ah oo wanaagsan. Sida baarax geel, kayga waa loo biltiriyaaye.
baarax: (tilmaame) bayaan iyo madmadoobi la'aan. Bishaarooyinkii Eebbahey, baarax aan u sheego. Dh: bayaan, tartiib.
baaray: (fal) baar ka dhig; ka dhig wax sare oo fiican. Dh: baaree.
baarayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baar ka dhigid; ka dhigidda wax sare oo wacan.
baarbaarri: (fal) si nabad iyo degganaansho leh u soco; si xarrago ah u soco. Ninkii ladan baa baarbaarriyee, miyaan Barniyey hurdo beegsanaayaa. Dh: tamashlee, daanshadaanshoo.
baarbaarrid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) daanshadaanshood iyo tamashlayn; socod ladnaansho ka muuqdo. Baarbaarrid beryaha abaareed kuuma qummana. Dh: daanshadaanshood, tamashleyn.
baarbaarrin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) daanshadaanshood iyo tamashlayn. Dh: baarbaarrid.
baarbaarritaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) samaynta baarbaarridda lafteeda iyo tamashlaynta. Baarbaarritaankii beryahan waan ka baaqsadaye.
baarcad: -da: (magacwadareed) awrta aan la raran weli ama la laylyin. Baarcad dhiilaha ninkii ku raray saw ma caramoobin. Dh: baarqab, baarfuran.
baarcadde: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ciyaar loo tumo qofka saarku hayo oo jiib iyo jabaq habdhac qurxoon leh oo raggu ciyaaro geeraar iyo midho qurxoonna hay ku sigibtiraan kolkolla habluhu sacabka u giijiyaan. Waa ciyaar qadiimi ah oo caan ku ah gobollada Waqooyi Galbeed, Galgaduud, Togdheer, Awdal iyo meelo kale. Qalabka lagu tumo ama loo qaato waxaa ka mid ah durbaan yar iyo ul yar oo lagu tumo iyo jeedal lagu dheelo. Ninka baarcaddaha loo tumaa wuxu yidhaa: kolka la isoo galgalaayo wilaalbaa i garab jooga golxad bay igu hayaan.
baarcadde -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ninka hoobalka ah laftiisa. Baayir waa baarcadde ciyaar badan.
baarcadde -ha: (magac, lab, keli) geed nagaadheed baxsha ubax cad oo qurux badan.
baare: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) cid wax inay baadho lagu og yahay. Dh: baadhe.
baarfuran: (tilmaame) qaalinka ama awrka aan weli la laylyin. Li: karinle.
baari: (fal) noqo wax baarixi ah ama baryood ah: noqo wax waqtigii la cuni lahaa ama la iibsan lahaa dhaafay
baari: (fal) madal naado wax lagu gadanayo, qiimo fican oo la gaadhay ku ka sii sarreeya ku eri; sicir barar ku rid. Ninka baayacii danbaa lagu baaryey ee qiimo fiican buu gaadhay.
baari -ga: (magac, lab, keli) saamaynta riixidda xooggeedu leeyahay; miisaanka culayska ee riixideed. Riixidda baarigeedu ma fufuda.
baari -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax lagu tartamayo iibsigiisa, kolba qofka naadadu ku dhacayso sida xaraashka. Baqashanu waa baariye yaa gadan.
baari: (tilmaame) wax xilligiisii dhaafay. Dh: baarixi, baryood. Li: daray.
baarid: baarid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) badeeco meel fagaare ah lagu munaadaynayo, qofka qiimaha ugu sarreya sheegay u xukumid.
baarid -ka: (magac, lab, keli) badeeco baartay kolka suuqa la geeyay, cid gadatana la waayey.
baarin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) badeeco la naadiyay qof u xukumid.
baaris: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax magan raadin. Dh: baadhis.
baaris -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) tijaabista la hubiyo wax in uu hirgelayo iyo inkale. Dh: tijaabis.
baaritaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax dahsoon raadin ku suubbin. Dh: baadhitaan.
baarixi: (fal) ka dhig wax baarixiyoobay ama la iibsan waayay. Baarixi badeecaddaada, berri bay qaaliyoobaysaaye.
baarixi -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax la iibinayey oo habeen ka dumay; badeecad maalintii loogu talo galay iibsami weyday oo subaxii danbe la lib keeno. Dh: baari, baryood.
baarixin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka dhigitaanka baryood xilligii la iibsan lahaa ama la cuni lahaa dhaafay.
baariyid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xilligii la isticmaali lahaa dhaafid. Dh: baaryid.
baarjeex: (tilmaame) badhtanka timo ka kala seeran ama ka kala rogan; timo dhexda ka kala jeexan.
baarjeexid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) timo dhaadheer badhtanka ka kala seexin; kala rogidda timaha oo badhtanka lagu kala jeexo. Baarjeexid baa laygu yaqaan taniyo yaridiiye, maatana waa la tirin karaa timaha guudkayga.
baarlamaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gole ka kooban mudaneyaal ama xildhibaanno dadku soo doortaan oo u qaabilsan sharcidejinta dal lagu maammulo iyo ilaalinta siyaasadda guud ee dalkaasi leeyahay.
baarleex: magaca wiil timo jilicsan oo qurxoon oo jiifa leh; wiil timihiisu bis jiifta yihiin.
baarniin: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) baadhitaan samayn iyo raadinta wax maqan. Dh: baadhniin.
baaro: (fal) iskaa u doondoono; iskaa u daydayo wax aad rabto inaad hesho. Baaro oo wixii ku cajibiya ka qaado dukaanka. Dh: baadho.
baaro: (fal) 'geel' jiif ku galgalo; ku rafo oo faadhumayso. Hashii rimmanayd gelgelintay baaranaysaa. Dh: galgalo, isrogrog.
baaro -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cadka yar ee wiilasha buuryadooda laga jaro marka la gudayo. Baarada wiilka well lagama jarin oo lama xalaalayn. Dh: ballanji, hanjaf.
baarobeeg: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qalab lagu cabbiro cadaadiska atmosfeerka. Dh: cadaadisbeeg.
baaroo: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) geed sida geelcadhaysta waaweyn u baxa oo cuntada lagu karsado; jaad ka mid ah khudradda la cuno ama faxfaxa iyo suugadaba lagu sameeyo.
baarqab: magac ama naanays loo baxsho wiil la filayo inuu sida awr baarqab ah yeesho raganimo iyo santaag.
baarqab: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) awrka aan la raran ee geela abaahiya. Baqas adhiya boqolaalka geel, baarqab iyo goolal. Dh: qoodh.
baarramid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) afeefasho oo cudurdaar sii qaddimasho, ballamid. Baarramid hore haddaad lahayn adkayso. Dh: baarrimasho, afeefasho.
baarran: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadal caadi ah ku sheekaysi. Si fiican baa xalay loo baarramay.
baarran: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadal sii teelladhigasho ah. Dh: afeef, shardi, ballan.
baarranaad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) afeefashada wax laga afeefto oo laga shardamo. Baarranaadka hadalkeennu waa kow dheh, beentiyo isdhaaf-dhaafku waa belo dheh.
baarranaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ahaanta wax afeef leh oo shardi ku xidhan yahay. Baarranaanta hadalkiyo baylahdeenna ilaali.
baarranaw: (fal) wax laga afeeftay oo shardi leh ahaw. Baarranaw intaanad hadal. Dh: afeefnaw.
baarrax: (tilmaame) erey la yidhaa marka beeli sheegayso oggolaanshaha heshiis nabadeed oo ay beel kale la gasho. Haddaan nahay ree qudhac, baarax baan nahay. Dh: oggol.
Baarre: magac loo baxsho wiil qurux badan oo dhirta caleenteeda cusub la wadaaga bilicda ama dhererka iyo toosnida.
baarre: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ubbooyinka subagga lagu dhigto jaad ka mid ah.
baarri: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ubbo calool weyn oo subagga lagu shubto. Dh: qunbe, tebbed.
baarri -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qofka yeela amarka labada waalid ee dhalay; qofka u dheganuglaada labadiisa waalid. Baarrigu janaduu galaa. Dh: muddeec, ducaqabe. Li: waalidinkaar, caaq.
baarrimad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) afeef sii dhigasho; Intaanad hadal horteed baarrimaad dhigto.
baarrimasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax aan weli dhicin, ka sii afeefasho.
baarrimo: (fal) hadalkaaga hortii afeefo oo eed, khalad iyo denbi ka sii gaashaamo. Hadalkaaga hortii baarrimo afafkaagana ood dhigo. Dh: afeefo, baarran.
baarrimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadal hortii afeefo oo cudurdaar sii samaysasho. Dacwaddaada hortii baarrimo dhigo. Dh: afeef, baarran.
baarrimo -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cudurdaarasho iyo afeef la sii qaddinto inta aan talo gaadhin. Baarrimada Yaasiin waa la wada ogaa. Dh: afeef.
baarrimo -ha: (magacwadareed) laba baad oo leebabka ama gantaalaha xagga dambe lagaga sameeyo si ay xawaaraha u dheereeyaan. Leebka intaanad ganin baarrimo ku xidh. Dh: baarrumo.
baarrimo -ha: (magacwadareed) xirribaha isha labadeeda dhinac ku yaal. Suubban waa gabadh baarrimo waaweyn. Dh: baarrumo, xirribo
baarrimow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qofka afmaalka ah ee hadalka yagaan. Samatar waa nin baarrimow ah
baarrinimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baarri ahaan: waalid'addeec ahaan. Baarrinimada jannadaa lagu galaa.
baarro: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) weel laga gooyo ubbada oo qooshka lagu sameeyo. Qarso jaadka laga gooyo iyo qude intaan haysto, ee gooshka baarrada ku jira laga qadaynaayo, maxaan bari ka qoollaaliyaa, waaban qabanayne.
baarro -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dermo la falkiyey oo midabaysan. Dh: dermo, caw, bal.
baarrumayn: -ta: (macac, dhedig, keli) leebka oo loo sameeyo baalal uu ku duulo oradka na ku badiyo oo uu yoolkiisa ku gaadho. Bal iga hooya weligayba waan baarrumayn jiraye.
baarrumo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) labo baal oo leebka xaggiisa danbe lagaga xidho si xawaaraha uu u dheereeyo. Dh: baalal.
baarrun: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) leebka xaggiisa dambe baad shimbireed yar oo loogu xidho si uu xawaarihiisa orodka u biiriyo.
baarrun -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) midho ama ubax si urursan oo cufan geedka baarkiisa uga baxa. Baarrun ubaxa iyo badhi bariday kala udgoon badane. Dh: rucub. rooshaan.
baaruc: -a: (magac, lab, keli) diimis iyo nagas isgalay oo ceel dhex fadhiya oo ur leh. Goofka baarucay, ey biyo hurdaan, daraaddaa baa, loogu daaloo, looga daba tegey, dilla gooryare.
baarug: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax kaste oo bata, oo barakooba, sida badarka la kariyo.
Baaruud: magac loo baxsho wiil la filayo inuu noqdo dagaalyahan ama mid diirdiirran oo firfircoon.
baaruud: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) walax qaraxda oo olol bixisa. Waxa loo adeegsadaa oo lagu dhex guraa rasaasta, bambooyinka iyo miinooyinka qarxa. Baarka baarkiisow, baaruudda ololka dheer low, hoy beeryarow 'e' dheh. Haaruudda qaraxdiyo bambaa laygu bilbilaaye.
baaryid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhaafitaanka xilligii la cuni lahaa ama la iibsan lahaa.
baaryid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax naado ama xaraash lagu iibinayo oo loo daynayo qofka gaadha qiimaha ugu wacan. Baaryidda ku horreeya idinku, annagu waan idinku xigaynnaaye.
baaryid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoog iyo culays saarid; riixid iyo xoog saamayn leh.
baaryoomid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) doonni ama markab deked ka furasho oo ka goosasho.
baaryoon: -ka: (magic, lab, keli) furashada doonyaha ama maraakiibtu ay dekedda ka furtaan ama ka goostaan. Dh: furasho, goosasho.
baas: (fal) itixaan ka qudub; itixaanka ka dallac; ka gudub fasal oo mid kale u dallac.

baas -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhib iyo waxyeello baas badan oo daran; wax aan dheef iyo wanaag lahayn. Balaayoy baydh, baasaw bax, barkhad Allay soo hoyo. Dh: belaayo, ba', balanbal, basanbaas, jab, masiibo, hankaag, hiirtaley, hoog. Li: barkhad, khayr
baas -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qoriga oo darandoorri baash rasaasta u rida.
baas -ka: (magac, lab, keli) tebinta labada ciyaartoy ay kubbadda isku tebiyaan ama isa siiyaan.
baasabbaasayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, been ku maaweelin; waxaan jirin ku meermeerin. Baasabbaasaynta hadalkiyo, been baad ku waasheen, bilistiyo carruurtee.
baasabbaasee: (fal) cid kale been ku meermeeri, wax aan jirin ku maaweeli.
baasaboor: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) waraaqadda aqoonsiga ee dalkumarka.
baasarce: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) noocyada bariiska, jaad ka mid ah, oo dhadhan wanaagsan leh.
baasaysad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) nicid wax la naco iyada oo la rumaysan yahay inuu dhibaato iyo xumaan horseed u yahay. Soomaali badan ayaa baasaysadka ci'da qambaarka iskaga mid ah.
baasaysasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka dhigashada wax baas leh oo belo ah.
baasayso: (fal) ka dhigo wax kuu ba'as oo hoog iyo belo leh.
baasaysi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) rumayn la rumeeyo in shay uu mar walba xumaan horseed u yahay. Baasaysiga qambaarku waa xujo aan daliil loo hayn.
baase: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) belada iyo colaadda aad u daran ee wax galaafata. Baase Allaw naga xijaab. Dh: hoog.
baashaal: (fal) tamashle wakhtiga isku dhaafi; ismadaddaali oo waqtiga wax isku dhaafi. Intay baashaalaysay buu itixaankii dhaafay
baashaal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ismadaddaalinta aanay hawli kuu oollin.
baashaal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) jalbeebka iyo sheekaysashada. Dh: haasaawe.
baashaali: (fal) mashquuli oo kolba wax ku maaweeli. Dh: maaweeli, mashquuli.
baashaalin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) maaweelin oo wakhtidhaaf u samayn. Dh: maaweelin.
baashaalitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) maddadaalo iyo maaweelo samayn.
baashad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) waraaq labadeeda dhan. Dh: bayaad, waraaq.
baashad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dilka cadawga darajo ku doonid; baal ku gashad.
Baashan: magac loo baxsho gabadh lagu faaninayo inay leedahay saansaanyihii iyo astaamihii bogoradaha.
Baashane: magac loo baxsho wiil ay ka muuqdaan calaamadihii madaxnimo ama loogu ducaynayo inuu noqdo boqor.
baashay: (fal) baabbacada gacanta ku salaax oo dhunko. Aadan waa nin naxariis badan oo carruurta gacana ku baasheeya. Dh: baashee.
baashayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhunkasho iyo salaaxid. Baashayntu ubadka way barbaarisaa.
baashe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) darajo turkiyeed la siiyo ciidammada; nin meel sare jooga ama haysta. Dayib, illaa heer baashe ayuu gaadhay.
baashe -ha: (magac, lab, keli) kolka turubka la ciyaarayo, warqadda sarraynta labaad leh.
Baashe: magac loo baxsho wiil la rajaynayo in uu noqdo nin madax ah.
Baashi: magac loo baxsho wiil la rajaynayo inuu noqdo madax taliya.
baashi: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhunkasho iyo gacan ku salaaxid ay naxariisi weheliso.
baashin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhunkashada iyo gacan ku salaaxidda ay naxariistu weheliso.
baashir: (fal) la wadaag sheeko, adiga oo u qalbi furan. Aan booyaamo xalay baa hurdadda, Leyla baashiray e.
baashir: (fal) weji furan iyo farxad kaga hortag qof la soo dhoweynayo oo marti ah. Isagaana baashiray yarkii boqorka loo saaray.
baashir -ka: (magac, lab, keli) soo dhoweynta dadka la jecel yahay iyo qaabilaaddooda. Farduus waa qof baashirka ku fiican.
baashiraad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) weji furan iyo farax ku soo dhoweynta iyo qaabilaadda qof marti ah.
baasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhunkasho iyo gacanta oo qof naxariis loogu salaaxo. Baashadu carruurta way barbaarisaa.
baasid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka gudbidda itixaan iyo waxii la mid ah.
baasiin: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) shidaal fudud oo degdeg u daarma, haddii la laydhiyana dhakhso u baabi'i og. Gaadhiga baasiin ku shub. Dh: bensiin, bansiin, betrool, baadrool, batrool.
baasitaan: baasitaan -ka: (magac, lab, keli) ku guulaysashada itixaan aad martay.
baaskiil: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gaadiid labo shaag iyo silsilad rogta leh oo cagta lagu wareejiyo. Mal laha mootoor, hal qof baana inta badan fuula. Aabbahay baa baabuur leh, anaa baaskiil leh baa dhaanta. Dh: buskuleeti, bushkuleeti.
baas'sheeg: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qof waxa xun oo keliya sheega oo belo ka warrama.
baas'sheegid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax xun oo keliya sheegid. Baas'sheegid iyo belo Allow naga ahay.
baasto: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) daqiiqda oo la engejiyay cunto laga sameeyo. Waxa loo sameeyaa si kala duwan oo leh qaar miiqmiiqsan, qaar balballaadhsan iyo kuwo dhexda daldaloola.
baastomiir: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) weel shaandho ah oo baastada la kariyey lagu shubo oo biyaha lagaga miiro.
baastoolad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qalab hubka fudfudud ka mid ah oo siddaha loo sudho suunka dhexda lagu xidho oo inta badan qaadda lix rasaasood oo yaryar.
baasuuke: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qori hal qof qaado oo xabbado waaweyn oo baaruud badani ku jirto ka dhacdo. Waxa lagula dagaallamaa taangiyada iyo gaadhiyada gaashaaman.
baati: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dhar jilicsan oo midabbo leh. Baati u soo gad gabadha la aroosayo. Dh: shiid
baatir: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qaalin aad u naaxday oo awrqaad ah; qaalin geel ah oo garabweyn Dh: abeer.
baatul: (fal) ha tashiilin hana bcekhaainin. Dh: bulqaas, yaree, gaabi.
baatul: (fal) cid ama wax kale, baabi'i ama burburi. Keenediid Bitikhan waysagi, gaas ku baatulaye Dh: maaruq, dabargoo, cabarjar. Li: dhao.
baatul -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhaqualocarrayn zan madax loo yeelin.
baatulan: (tilmaame) wax la baatulay oo aan la tashiilin; wax aan la mitamin ama dadkii lahaa dayacay. Xoolo baatulan magacood baa ba'ay. Dh: bay:imaal, baylahsan. Li: ilaashan, dhawran.
baatulid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ashiilla'aan yu baatul ku samayn. Reatulid berri kuma gaadhsiiso. Dh: haatulis.
baatulitaan: -ka: (magac, lah, keli) baytimaalin iyo daadaadin siyaado ah..
baatulmid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolo, si israaf iyo tashillid la'aan ah ku bixid. Lacatiisii baatulmid bay ku dhammaatay.
baatulnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) israafid iyo tashilic la'uan. Ninka xooiihiisa baatulaan ku bidyaa berri ayuu gartaa.
baatulnow: (fal) wax baatulan; nogo wax aan la tashilin. Li: tashilnow.
baawa: -ha: magac, lab, kel) buuq iyo qaylo golka la leexiya ama ka mashquuliya howshii uu gacanta ku hayay, ama wuxiu maskaxda kala socday.
baawasiir: -ta: (magne, dhedig, keli) nabarre cuncun, barar iyo xanuun badan oo malwadka at siisa kasoo baxa, inta badanna dhiig ka yimaaddo. Walle nimay baawasiir haysaar barbar u fadhiisan waayin. Dh: haawaasiir, baabusit, mabaasiir.
baaway: (fal) gaadhsii dad badan; ogaysii ummadda oo dhan. Dh: baafin.
baawee: (fall baylihi oo wax bilaa daryeel ah ka dhig. Xoolahaaga haddaad doonto baawec oo waxa dadweynaha ilaali. Dh: haawey, halladaadi.
baaweyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) xog, war ama wax kale oo meel ku koobnaa, dad badan gaadhsiintiisa.
baawirad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) jaad noocyada tawaariista ka mid ah oo labo ulood leh.
baaxaaddeg: baaxaaddeg -ga: (magac, lab, keli) go'aan qaadan waa; dhanna xaminili waa. Berraan dhoofi lahaaye, baaya baaxaaddeg baan ku jiraa.
baaxaaddeg -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qof qarqoomay oo ay biyo liqeen; qof kolba mawjad gelaya oo kolla kor u soo baxaya kolla hoos u dhaadhacaya. Baaxaaddeg buu biyaha kor iyo hoos u gelayaa.
baaxaaddegan: (tilmaame) mid aan degganayn oo aan xaaldba ku sugnayn.
baaxaaddegid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kolba dhinac u geddoomid oo degganaanshaha waayid.
baaxaalli: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) habdhaqanka iyo dabciga qofka Ilaahay ku abuuray; dabeecad aan xin iyo xajiin toona lahayn.
baaxaallideg: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dabciga qofka oo isbedbeddela.
baaxad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) balladhka iyo kala baxsanaan. Dh: ballac, balladh.
baaxad -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) awood iyo tamar weyn. Haddaan baaxad leeyahay, badda saw ma jiidheen. Dh: quwad, awood, xoog.
baaxadsoore: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) dhul ballaadhan oo baaxadweyn badhtamihiisa; dhul kala fidsan meesha kala badha. Saw baaxadsoorehii iyo lababoglayntii, maan noqon bestay oo, bacadkii ma dheelliman.
baaxadsoore -ha: (magac, lab, keli) xilliga duhurka ee ay cadceedduna aadka u kulushahay. Baaxad-soore iyo adigaan ka biqin baabullaha aare. Dh: yoomayoome.
baaxeer: (tilmaame) qof bashaash ah oo weji furan.
baaxuur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) caws la bah ah cawsqurunka oo rarada laga sameeyo xooluhuna daaqaan. Waaryaa badhiwayne, baaxuurow ba'aw, bilicdaa ma leedahay. Dh: badhiwayne.
baaxuur -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qof karti iyo awood badan oo arrin iyo aqoon ba leh. Dh: carceer.
baaxuur -ka: (magac, lab, keli) daayeerka kiisa coofaadhka ah ee gaboobay. Dh: daaxuur.
baayaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) darxumo badan; ba' iyo hoog.
baayac: (fal) weydii qiimaha wax aad rabto iibsashadiisa. Intaanad iibsan iska baayac raashinka.

aanneen: -aanneen v5a-1pl-neg-cond • we would not have been. Maannu ogaanneen We would not have known.
aannin: -aannin v5a-neg-opt • may [someone] not be ... Yaanu ogaannin! Dont let him be aware of it!
aanno: -aanno v5a-1pl-opt • may we be, let us be ... Haddii uun aynu ladnaanno! If only we would be healthy!
aansho: -aansho vn6-m-st-suf • state of being (X); -ation [GERUND] Makes a masculine stative verbal noun toddobaadkii dambe last week sannadkii dambe last year; Contrast: -ka.
aanu: 1 neg + vpro • he ... not = aan + uu.
aar: aar1 n4-m • adult male lion; [fig.] brave man
aar2 Compare: saajac vn0-m-col • revenge, vengeance.
aaraa': n8-f-pl • ideas, opinions; [ext.] preface, introduction (of a book)
aarad: n1-f • edge ~ border of an Arab robe
aaradee: v2b=tr • make the border for something (e.g., clothes)
aaran: aaran1 n0-m-abs • abundance of water and green grass; prosperity, flourishing natural environment
aaran2 n2a-m-col • young camels who are no longer sucklings, camel youth
aargalaan: n2-m • large cup ~ glass; metal cup with a handle
aarsasho: vn6-f • vengeance, act of taking revenge
aas: -aas deic-m-suf • that, those On masculine nouns
aas1 n4-m • colorful light of sunset.
aasan: aasan1 v1=inch • be buried, get buried
aashaa: np / adv • you ... slowly, gently, carefully
aashay: np / adv • I ... slowly, gently, carefully Aashay baan u akhriyey. I read it carefully.
aasheed: np / adv • she ... slowly, gently, carefully Aasheed bay hilibkii u karisay. She cooked the meat slowly.
aashuun: n2-m • water-jar made of clay; jug
aatee: -aatee v5a-2sg/3f-pot • suppose you are / so she may be ...
aateen: -aateen1 v5a-2pl-opt • may you all be! Waan filayaa in aydin jeclaateen! I hope that you like it!
-aateen2 v5a-2pl-pot • suppose you all are / so you may be ...
-aateen3 v5a-neg-cond • you / she would not have been.
aato: -aato v5a-2sg/3f-opt • may you / she be Maxaad ku tashateen? What did you decide on? Ku tasho inaad ila joogto. Count on staying at my place.
aawadeed: np / conj • because of, for its sake After a feminine noun Tigidh la'aan awadeed ayaan u tegi waayey. I failed to go because I didn't have a ticket.'
aawadiis: Compare: aw np / conj • because of, for its sake After a masculine noun Roob badan awadiis wadooyiinkii oo dhan daad baa xidhay. Because of heavy rain, a flood closed all the streets.
aaway: aaway1 qw-loc-m • where is he / it [masc]?
aawo: n0-f • sake, reason Used with possessive pronouns
aay: -aay1 name-f-voc-suf • hey you! [FEMININE VOCATIVE] Used to call or address a female barad trainee dhunkad act of kissing haysad possessing.
aayad: aayad2 Compare: mucjiso n1-f • miracle, wonder
aayar: Compare: aad yar Adverb • slowly, gently, lightly, slightly
aaye: aaye1 n6-f • aunt, uncle's wife; stepmother
aayeen: -aayeen v5a-3pl-past • they were Wey fiicnaayeen. They were fine.
aayo: aayo4 n6-f • aunt, uncle's wife; stepmother
ab: ab1 n4-m, n7-m • ancestor; [pl] forefathers, ancestry.
ab2 n2-m-cmp, n7-m • native (of a place); locals; tradition, heritage.
abaab: v1= • scatter on; crawl, creep, move along by creeping; walk (as reptile ~ insect).

a: df.art., the, (af) used with its support.
á, ad., this, that, (af) used with its support.
aal: or ahal, f.n., slime or viscous matter mixed with blood (in dysentery).—shi.
‘ab: v.tr., drink (this verb is used for any liquid except milk, coffee, and broth); biyaha “ab, drink water; dawada ‘ab, drink the medicine; biyo ‘ab o hamri iss ka da, drink water and not wine; biyaha la 'ab, the water is drunk.
‘absi: v.c., cause or give to drink ; i ‘absi, make me or give me to drink.
'abād: m.n., camels grunting (while its burden is fastened on). —ki; aur ‘abādked ma je‘li, I do not like the camel’s grunting.
abah: m.n., time of birth.—hi: hashi nerig bai abahha ku dashai or dalatai, the she-camel brought forth her young one.
abaḥ: m.n., lean animal. —hi; aurkasi wa geli abaḥah, that camel is lean.
abaḥ, v.i., be lean ;wu abiḥi, he will be lean.
‘abai: v.tr., load a gun; bunduha ‘abai, load the gun.
abāl: m.n., gratitude, acknowledgment, remuneration, requital. —ki; abālka ān ku (pi. idin) habo or haiyo weligi wu jiri, my gratitude for you will last forever; hadiyadda an ku so diro wa abālkan ku haba or haiya, the gift I send you is an acknowledgment; wa abalké, it is your requital; abal u hab, be grateful; abal ban ad ugu habai or abal ada yan u habai, I was very grateful to him; wahhasi wa abalkai, it is for my gratitude.
abālgud: u abālgud, v.tr., reward; i abālgud, reward me; wan ku abālgudai, I rewarded you.
abālgudi: v.tr., reward (only used by some, especially by people from the west)
abālmari: v.tr., be grateful, thank, reward. —ya or abālmarsha, —wan n; aniga abbaha abālmariyai, I was grateful to the father.
abar: f.n., drought, sterility, famine. —ti ; bilad somalied abar ba ka da'dai or bilad somalied o dami abar wa lehyahai, there is everywhere drought in the Somali country; wa abar, there is famine; abarta meshas ka da'dai ad ba lo ogyahai, the sterility of that place is well known.
abba: m.n., father. —hi ; aiya abba, or abbai, or abbo! my father.
abban: m.n.f friend, protector, guide, conductor. —ki; (guest and host are abban;) abban dulai, m.n., chief, leader.
abbanso: v.r., become friends with ; ninkas abbanso, put yourself under the protection of that man, or become friends with that man.
'abbar: m.n., moment, short time, a while. —ki; 'abbar jog, wait a moment ; 'abbar la hadso, sit a moment with him.
abhad: f.n., small box made with the bark of trees tacked together. —di.
abho: f.n., fruit of a thorny tree called huda', of which sheep and goats are very fond.
abid: and abki, ad., never (these words are never employed alone as given, but inflected according to the person speaking or spoken of (s. gram.).
abodi: m.n., large bird of prey, having a red beak and red legs. —gi
abor: m.n., Bpeoies of white ants making their hills or houses in the desert. —ki.
'abso: v.i., be afraid or frightened. —da, wan —n.
'absileh: a., dangerous, perilous; war! mel 'absileh ina gei, take us to a dangerous place.
abti: m.n., maternal uncle. —gi; or hoyada walalked, the mother's brother.
abtirsinyo: m.n., genealogy. -hi; 'Issa abtirsinyihisi, the genealogy of Jesus.
‘abud: v.tr., adore ; ha lagu 'abudo, be thou adored.
abud: v.tr., shut, close (employed lor small boxes), cork a bottle abhadda abud, shut or close the box ; haruradda abud.
'abud: v.tr., suffocate ('abudi is also used by some).
abur: m. or f.n., behaviour, conduct, temper. —ki or —ti; aburkisu wa side? how does he behave? aburkisu wa sida, he behaves so; abur fi'an, good temper; abur hun, bad temper.
aburan: v.p., be produced, created; aburma, wan abtirmi, wan aburmai, I was created.
aburan, m.n., creation. —ki; aburnin. —ti, f.n., is also used.
aburan, a.v., created; wah aburan, a created thing.
ad: a. and ad., well, nice, good, loud, strong (this word is an adverb when u is added to it. Ex. kitabkas wa ad, that book is nice; ad u tol, sew well; ad u hadal, speak well or loudly; ad u adkai, make it strongly; ad u dis, build well.
'ad: m.n., piece of meat, flesh. —ki (the plural 'adad is not used by all) ; 'adki i dib, give me the piece of meat ; 'adki i wada ken or 'adadki i ken, bring me the pieces of meat.
'adaw: v.att., be, become white (no imperative) ; wan 'adan. (When this verb is used in the imperative, it is a kind of curse.)
'adaisnaw: v.att., remain or be white, clean; distigu wa 'adaisanyahai, the kettle is made white or cleansed.
'adaisan: a.v.,made white, cleansed; maro 'adaisan, clean linen.
'adab: f.n., hell. —ti. ; 'adab yar, purgatory. dab 'adabed, m.n., hell fire. —ki.
'adab or 'adib, v.tr., torment, torture; 'adab means also condemn to hell.
'adad: fn., kind of acacia tree with stiff and bent thorns, gum-tree. —di.
adad: m.n., excrescence of flesh in a sore. —ki.
'adadi: 'adadi, v.tr., press. (In the jungle Somals, when making their enclosure or fence round their huts, press together the trees cut for that purpose, in order that the branches may be straight, so as to form a close and tough hedge.)
adag: a., dear (price), fast firm, hard, strong, light, tough, permanent. (This word is used for things only.)
adkai: v.tr., fasten, strengthen, tighten, make strong. ha lagu adka, v.p., be fastened.
adkaw: v.att., be firm, strong, fastened. ka adkaw, v.a., overcome him, her; ka adka, he overcomes, overcame him ; ka adkatai, she overcomes, overcame ; wa laga adka, adkadai, he, she is overcome.
adai: m.n., arak tree (Capparis sodata), small stick used by Somals for cleaning their teeth. -gi.
'adanyo: 'adanyo or 'adanyod, v.i., have an itching. —da, wan —n.
'adar: 'adar, m.m., haziness, hazy weather, drizzling rain. —ki (no plur.) 'adar da, it drizzles or drizzling rain is falling.
adar: m.n., earthen pot with two handles in which food is cooked. —ki.
'ad'ed: f.n, rays of the sun, sun. —di; eg! 'ad'eddi da'dai, look! the sun is setting; war! 'ad'eddi so bahdai, ina kena, mesha ka so'onai, the rays of the sun appear, let us go away from the place. —di.
aderyo 'ari: lesser koodoo antelope (used for both genders). N.B. Somals generally make no difference between aderyo and aderyo 'ari. They call the males godir, and the females aderyo.
adin: adin, v.tr., call to prayer ; adima, wan adimi.
'aḋo: f.n., anger, indignation, rage, wrath (no plur.).
'ado, v.i., rage. —da, wan —n. u 'ado, v.tr., rage against.
'aḋaisi: with ka, v.c, provoke, make him angry, enrage.
af badan: a., sharp ; mindi af badan, a sharp knife.
af daran: a., blunt; mindidi afka daraid i ken, bring me the blunt knife.
afdub: afdub, m.n., closing of the mouth to prevent a man from crying out when they rob his cattle and sheep. —ki ; ninkas afdubkisi mid ad u aha, the gagging of that man was good.
af'eli: v.tr., interpret (this verb is used with uga, ka, or u ka la); wan u ka la af'elin, I interpret or I will interpret.
aftiro: v.tr., wipe your lips ; aftirta, wan aftiran. Somals also use aftiro for 'take some food.'
afyahan: m.n. and a., eloquent, eloquent man, tame. —ki; aniga afyahan miihi, I am not eloquent, or not an eloquent man; faras afyahan, a tame horse dinnad aftahan, a tame cat dinnaddi afkatihin, the tame cat.
afarr: n.c, four.—ti; afarr nagod, four women.
afrad: n.c.o., fourth; ki afrad (m.), the fourth.
afarr iyo tobnad: n.c.o., fourteenth, a fortnight ; afarr iyo tobnadki, the fortnight.
'affi: 'affi, m.n., forgiveness, pardon. —gi. war! iss 'affiya, v.r., pardon each other (plur.)
afimad: m.n., health. —ki; ma afimad habta? are you in good health? ha wa ladnahai, yes I am.
afo: f.n., woman, lady; afada serkalka, the wife of the governor.
afur: m.n., a small meal taken at about six o'clock in the evening during the time of fasting, while the muezzin is calling Mussulmans to prayer. The other meal, taken from 12 p.m. to 4 a.m. is called suhur.
'agta'ad: f.n., foot-sole; agti 'adaid, the sole of the foot.
ag: ad., near (this word is never used alone) ; agta, agtaida kalai, come near (me) ; agtisi tag, go near (to him).
agan: f.n., bark vessel (shaped like a double cone, and protected by a light framework of wood called sab). —ti.
agon: m.n., orphan boy. -ki (the plural for both sexes is agonadi).

agon, /.«., orphan girl. ti (this word is also used for both sexes) Berberah agonadu wa ku badanyihin, or Berberah agontu wa ku badantahai, or war Berberi wa agon badan tahai, there are many orphans in Berberah.
ah: (root) v., he (often used as an affix; scarcely ever alone).
ahaw: ha ahato, or ha ahatai e, loc. meaning nevertheless, never mind, be it so.
ahdi: m.n., oath, swearing, alliance, treaty made by an oath. -gi. ahdi Ebbahai inan ka kausin, I swear by God that I will kill you.

ahdi, v.tr., swear, make a treaty, an alliance grounded upon an oath; wa la iss ahdiyai o dagal ma jiro, I made a treaty that we may not fight; kal hore yainu iss ahdinai lakin ahdigi wa adigi beinaiyai, last year we made a treaty, but you perjured yourself, or you did not remain faithful to it.
ahal horti: m.n. fa9ade, house-front. -ki. ahalka hortisi bai jogan, or wa ku joga, they are before, or in front of, the house.

capodanno: s.m. maalinta ugu horreeysa ee sannadka cusub.
capolavóro: s.m. - wax qabad kan ugu wacan.
